  "text": "1 Children with CIs in general have low accuracy for the production of /s/ [CITATION_1] , and therefore, it is uncertain whether substitutions of other fricatives for /s/ (or for /$/ ) influenced the results of the acoustic analyses. The present study therefore examined the contrast between /s/ and /$/ only for productions that were transcribed as correct.",
